{"image_id": "IT_2008_page_137", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "The fair value of restricted stock, restricted stock units (RSUs), and common stock equivalents (CSEs) is determined", "bbox": [162.5, 87.3, 1093.7, 106.0]}, {"text": "on the date of grant based on the closing price of the Company’s common stock as reported by the New York Stock", "bbox": [162.5, 114.4, 1104.3, 133.1]}, {"text": "Exchange on that date. The fair value of these awards is recognized as compensation expense as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 141.5, 1014.0, 160.2]}, {"text": "(i) outstanding restricted stock awards vest based on the achievement of a market condition and are expensed on a", "bbox": [162.5, 168.5, 1092.0, 187.3]}, {"text": "straight-line basis over three years; (ii) service-based RSUs vest ratably over four years and are expensed on a", "bbox": [162.5, 195.6, 1045.7, 214.4]}, {"text": "straight-line basis over four years; (iii) performance-based RSUs are subject to both performance and service", "bbox": [162.5, 222.7, 1035.1, 241.5]}, {"text": "conditions, vest ratably over four years, and are expensed on an accelerated basis as required by SFAS No. 123(R);", "bbox": [162.5, 249.8, 1092.2, 268.5]}, {"text": "and (iv) CSEs vest immediately and are recorded as expense on the date of grant.", "bbox": [162.5, 276.9, 819.7, 295.6]}, {"text": "The Company recognized the following amounts of stock-based compensation expense for the years ended", "bbox": [162.5, 330.7, 1033.2, 349.5]}, {"text": "December 31 (in millions):", "bbox": [162.5, 357.8, 369.6, 376.6]}, {"text": "Award type:", "bbox": [162.5, 407.1, 248.9, 423.7]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [946.7, 407.1, 983.7, 423.7]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [1013.3, 407.1, 1050.4, 423.7]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [1075.4, 407.1, 1112.5, 423.7]}, {"text": "Restricted stock", "bbox": [162.5, 436.2, 279.1, 452.9]}, {"text": "$ 0.4", "bbox": [942.1, 436.2, 983.8, 452.9]}, {"text": "$ 1.8", "bbox": [1008.8, 436.2, 1050.5, 452.9]}, {